#: ../../../deploying-contracts.rst:6
msgid "Deploying a Contract"
msgstr "部署合約"

#: ../../../deploying-contracts.rst:8
msgid ""
"Once you are ready to deploy your contract to a public test net or the main "
"net, you have several options:"
msgstr "當您準備好將合約部署到公開測試網或主網時，您有幾個選項："

#: ../../../deploying-contracts.rst:10
msgid ""
"Take the bytecode generated by the vyper compiler and manually deploy it "
"through mist or geth:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../deploying-contracts.rst:12
msgid ""
"vyper yourFileName.vy\n"
"# returns bytecode"
msgstr ""
"vyper yourFileName.vy\n"
"# 回傳位元組碼"

#: ../../../deploying-contracts.rst:17
msgid ""
"Take the byte code and ABI and deploy it with your current browser on "
"`myetherwallet's <https://www.myetherwallet.com/>`_ contract menu:"
msgstr ""
"取得位元組碼和 ABI，並在 `myetherwallet <https://www.myetherwallet.com/>`_ 的"
"合約選單中使用您目前的瀏覽器進行部署："

#: ../../../deploying-contracts.rst:19
msgid ""
"vyper -f abi yourFileName.vy\n"
"# returns ABI"
msgstr ""
"vyper -f abi yourFileName.vy\n"
"# 回傳 ABI"

#: ../../../deploying-contracts.rst:24
msgid ""
"Use `Titanoboa <https://github.com/vyperlang/titanoboa/?tab=readme-ov-"
"file#network-mode>`_:"
msgstr ""
"使用 `Titanoboa <https://github.com/vyperlang/titanoboa/?tab=readme-ov-"
"file#network-mode>`_："

#: ../../../deploying-contracts.rst:26
msgid ""
"import boa\n"
"boa.set_network_env(<RPC URL>)\n"
"from eth_account import Account\n"
"# in a real codebase, always load private keys safely from an encrypted "
"store!\n"
"boa.env.add_account(Account(<a private key>))\n"
"deployer = boa.load_partial(\"yourFileName.vy\")\n"
"deployer.deploy()"
msgstr ""
"import boa\n"
"boa.set_network_env(<RPC URL>)\n"
"from eth_account import Account\n"
"# 在真實的程式碼庫中，請始終從加密儲存中安全地載入私鑰！\n"
"boa.env.add_account(Account(<a private key>))\n"
"deployer = boa.load_partial(\"yourFileName.vy\")\n"
"deployer.deploy()"

#: ../../../deploying-contracts.rst:36
msgid ""
"Use the development environment provided at https://try.vyperlang.org to "
"compile and deploy your contract on your net of choice. try.vyperlang.org "
"comes \"batteries-included\", with Titanoboa pre-installed, and browser "
"signer integration as well."
msgstr ""
"使用 https://try.vyperlang.org 提供的開發環境，在您選擇的網路上編譯和部署合"
"約。try.vyperlang.org 是「電池已附」的，預先安裝了 Titanoboa，並整合了瀏覽器"
"簽章器。"

#: ../../../deploying-contracts.rst:1
msgid "deploying"
msgstr "部署"

#: ../../../deploying-contracts.rst:1
msgid "deploying;"
msgstr "部署;"
